      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个物流库存状态的状态图。核心概念是Logistics_StockLevel，它有两种基本状态：静止（Still）和移动中（Moving）。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Still",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。Still和Moving都是Logistics_StockLevel的状态，那它们之间可以互相转换吗？比如从静止切换到移动，或者反过来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这两个状态是双向的。货物开始运输就从Still变成Moving，到达目的地卸货就从Moving回到Still。另外，Logistics_StockLevel本身既是入口也是出口，可以回到这个抽象层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画好了Still和Moving之间的双向箭头，以及它们与Logistics_StockLevel的连接。还有别的状态需要考虑吗？比如异常情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "非常重要的一点——运输过程中可能发生Crash（事故）。这是Moving状态的一个特殊出口，一旦发生事故，货物状态就变成Crash。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Crash",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Crash之后呢？是停留在Crash状态，还是可以恢复到其他状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "事故处理完后，货物信息要重新录入系统，所以Crash应该能回到Logistics_StockLevel这个顶层，相当于重新初始化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Crash",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
